    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>50% Visual Novel</strong><br><strong>50% Sci-Fi Karaoke-Musical </strong><br><strong>100% Existential - Wet - Bald - Cheesy</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>The world's first Sci-Fi Karaoke-Musical where your choices create the lyrics.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004410/extras/355f23ecc2492498442c30e1e500ff41.poster.avif?t=1771971551\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004410/extras/355f23ecc2492498442c30e1e500ff41.webm?t=1771971551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004410/extras/355f23ecc2492498442c30e1e500ff41.mp4?t=1771971551\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dystopian Sci-Fi Narrative</strong>: Emotional, strange, and a little absurd. Your choices don’t just shape the story, they <i>become the lyrics you’ll sing.</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hand-Drawn Art</strong>: Every scene drawn from Ozan’s imagination. <i>(The Holy Gosh Darn, Helheim Hassle, Manual Samuel).</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bangers</strong>: Actual bangers. By Bear &amp; Cat. <i>(Teslagrad, Teslagrad 2, World to the West, plus a gazillion stage musicals.)</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Fish</strong>: Your friend. Maybe.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Love</strong>: Potentially.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fully Voice-Acted</strong>: Except the lead. That’s your part!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sing as the Protagonist</strong>: Share your personality with friends or your streaming audience. Whether you’re singing for fun or going full performance mode!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004410/extras/6309807f991089fa672a87a5a92096a5.avif?t=1771971551\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004410/extras_big/6309807f991089fa672a87a5a92096a5.avif?t=1771971551 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Prepare for a trippy, emotional journey through an underwater world where adventure and absurdity collide. From the damp, moldy confines of your Seabase to the promise of a better life on Moonbase-3, you’ll brave cosmic wonders, emotional upheavals, and maybe even find love in the most unlikely places.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004410/extras/57c7a8378a84816545f21b8875528885.poster.avif?t=1771971551\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004410/extras/57c7a8378a84816545f21b8875528885.webm?t=1771971551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004410/extras/57c7a8378a84816545f21b8875528885.mp4?t=1771971551\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Love, loss, and songs await beneath the waves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004410/extras/ecd40fa268c0fd9352f3f7fc964db94e.avif?t=1771971551\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004410/extras_big/ecd40fa268c0fd9352f3f7fc964db94e.webp?t=1771971551 width=1560 height=2184 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">You create the story, and then you sing!</p>",
